did.unittitle: DeLaney Kiphuth, special assistant to the president of Yale University for athletics, Records

repository.corpname: Yale University. Department of Manuscripts and Archives

did.abstract: The records consist of applications, reports, correspondence, committee notes, budgets, films, studies, fellowships, questionnaires, and recommendations documenting Special Assistant DeLaney Kiphuth's interests concerning athletics at Yale University.

odd.head: General note
odd.p: Forms part of Yale Record Group 2-B (YRG 2-B), Records of Yale presidential assistants.

accessrestrict.head: Conditions Governing Access
accessrestrict.p: Access to the records is restricted. See inventory for details.

prefercite.head: Preferred Citation
prefercite.p: DeLaney Kiphuth, Special Assistant to the President of Yale University for Athletics, Records (RU 726). Manuscripts and Archives, Yale University Library.

processinfo.head: Processing Information
processinfo.p: Yale University records are arranged and described at the accession level by the creating office. The University Archives creates collection level descriptive records, but typically does no further arrangement and description at the accession level.

scopecontent.head: Scope and Contents
scopecontent.p: The records consist of applications, reports, correspondence, committee notes, budgets, films, studies, fellowships, questionnaires, and recommendations documenting Special Assistant DeLaney Kiphuth's interests concerning athletics at Yale University.

arrangement.head: Arrangement
arrangement.p: The records are arranged alphabetically by subject.
